# NorthStar Client Portal

## Project Overview
The NorthStar Client Portal is a server-rendered web application
developed using Node.js, Express.js, and EJS. The system dynamically
generates client interface pages using reusable layout templates and
a centralized JSON dataset. The application demonstrates consistent
interface structure, reusable components, and real-time rendering of
operational client records.

## Installation
npm install

## Run Application
node app.js

## Routes
/ → Home page  
/clients → Client directory  
/clients/:id → Individual client profile  

## Features Implemented
✔ Express server with EJS template engine  
✔ Shared layout using Express EJS Layouts  
✔ Reusable header, navigation, footer partials  
✔ Dynamic client list rendering  
✔ Dynamic client detail pages  
✔ Consistent styling across pages  
